title: Fix multiprocess download
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/pull/26 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
Bug fixes

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Fix multiprocess download. 
because of sleep. it hangs. 

comments from @guoshengCS :
鉴于目前 paddle 中的 get_path_from_url 接口在被多卡多进程调用时各进程并非严格意义上的竞争关系，实际上写死了只有某个确定的进程会去下载这个数据 https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/develop/python/paddle/utils/download.py#L152 ，这里也可以先不考虑文件锁，只让这个确定的进程去get_data并在完成后touch一个类似squad.done的文件，其他进程都在wait，wait时循环检测这个文件是否存在，存在的话就认为数据获取完成结束wait。这些逻辑可以加在get_data https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/blob/develop/paddlenlp/datasets/dataset.py#L508 前后

body:
网络的修改按照官网的说明修改的
`
```
import paddle.nn as nn
from paddlenlp.transformers import ErnieModel
from paddlenlp.layers import LinearChainCrf, LinearChainCrfLoss, ViterbiDecoder


class ErnieModelNew(ErnieModel):
    def __init__(self, ernie, num_classes=2, dropout=None, gru_hidden_size=128):
        super(ErnieModelNew, self).__init__(vocab_size=200)
        self.num_classes = num_classes
        # allow ernie to be config
        self.ernie = ernie
        self.dropout = nn.Dropout(dropout if dropout is not None else
                                  self.ernie.config["hidden_dropout_prob"])
        # add bi-gru
        self.gru = nn.GRU(
            input_size=self.ernie.config["hidden_size"],
            hidden_size=gru_hidden_size,
            direction='bidirect')
        self.fc = nn.Linear(
            in_features=gru_hidden_size * 2,
            out_features=num_classes)
        # add crf
        self.crf = LinearChainCrf(
            num_classes,
            with_start_stop_tag=False)
        self.crf_loss = LinearChainCrfLoss(self.crf)
        self.viterbi_decoder = ViterbiDecoder(
            self.crf.transitions,
            with_start_stop_tag=False)

```

    def forward(self,
                input_ids,
                token_type_ids=None,
                labels=None,
                position_ids=None,
                attention_mask=None):
        sequence_output, _ = self.ernie(
            input_ids,
            token_type_ids=token_type_ids,
            position_ids=position_ids,
            attention_mask=attention_mask)
        sequence_output = self.dropout(sequence_output)
        bigru_output, _ = self.gru(sequence_output)
        emission = self.fc(bigru_output)
        lengths = []
        for i,e in enumerate(emission):
            lengths.append(len(e))
        import paddle
        lengths = paddle.to_tensor(lengths, dtype='int64')
        _, prediction = self.viterbi_decoder(emission, lengths) # lengths 是batch size的大小
        # return prediction
        if labels is not None:
            loss = self.crf_loss(emission, lengths, prediction, labels)
            return loss, lengths, prediction, labels
        else:
            return input_ids, lengths, prediction
`

matmul | 0.9365 | 0.9017 | 0.5408 | 0.8817 / 0.8382 | 0.8381 / 0.8451 | 0.9095 / 0.8776 | 0.8615 / 0.8606 | 0.7004 | 0.9407
einsum | 0.9357 | 0.9024 | 0.5589 | 0.8861 / 0.8431 | 0.8524 / 0.8540 | 0.9080/ 0.8769 | 0.8639 / 0.8623 | 0.6967 | `1.1413`

The performance of BigBird improve from 25% to 40%.

title: Add tiny bert model
body:
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features
### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
- 重新定义了`MultiHeadAttention`,  `TransformerEncoderLayer`, `TransformerEncoder`的`forward`函数（为了定义用于蒸馏的`TinyBertModel`，`TinyBertModel`需要拿到每一层的attention_scores和每一层`TransformerEncoder`的输出
- 增加3个class: `TinyBertModel`,  `TinyBertForPretraining`,  `TinyBertForSequenceClassification`
- 以`TinyBertForSequenceClassification`为例，在fp64下，对齐和竞品的logits、及中间输出attention_output, sequence_output：
a.6l_768_dim下结果均能对齐；
b.6l_768_dim_v2下输出的 logits能对齐，中间输出部分少数tensor的最大相对diff数量级在n*1e-7；
c.4l_312d和4l_312d_v2下输出的logits能对齐，中间输出部分最大相对误差常是1e-2，1e-3的n倍(n:1-9)
d.不过，对于上面说的中间结果不符合预期的相对误差(数量级1e-2，1e-3），常发生在很小的数上（<1e-6)，且原因是【除以math.sqrt运算】放大了误差；
- 增加`to_distill`函数，绑定在带有transformer layer的layer子类对象上，调用之后可以获取中间transformer层的输出、attention matrix，以及embedding的输出
